you review the entire proxy statement you may retrieve the full proxy statement by going to the securities and exchange commission sec website at wwwsecgov and entering the companys name and then looking in the first column for an entry of form def a or any similar code you may also find the annual proxy statement by going directly to the companys website what is a proxy statement a proxy statement or proxy is a form that every publicly traded us company is required to file with the us securities  exchange commission sec within  days after the end of its fiscal year the proxy must be sent to every shareholder in advance of the companys annual shareholders meeting all proxy statements are public filings made available to the general public by the sec the proxy statements main purpose is to alert shareholders to the annual meeting and provide them information about the issues that will be voted on during the annual meeting including decisions such as electing directors ratifying the selection of auditors and other shareholderrelated decisions including shareholderinitiated initiatives also proxies must disclose specific detailed information regarding the pay practices for certain executives       privacy policy terms of use about us contact us  salarycom all rights reserved us salaries canadian salaries purchase a salary report salaries by category salaries by income salaries by industry popular salaries negotiation tips benefits calculator search job openings job openings by state job openings by category education by career education by level education by major cost of living calculator bruce hazelgrove jr obituary flowers directions contact bruce hazelgrove jr obituary view more obituaries bruce reginald hazelgrove jr january    september   contat us guestbook services flowers obituary hazelgrove bruce reginald jr born january   died september   he was the son of lucille m and bruce r hazelgrove sr and was predeceased by his sister jane lee h rollins he is survived by his wife of  years mary mcgrath hazelgrove his family mary bruce glaize and her husband phil sarah hazelgrove bruce r hazelgrove iii and his wife margaret and kevin lee beale and his wife beth bruce is survived by  grandchildren maggie lucy philip iii and david glaize burch bruce iv willie and anne stewart hazelgrove and thornton and marshall beale he was a lifelong member of centenary united methodist church serving on numerous committees mr hazelgrove was educated in the richmond city public schools and graduated from thomas jefferson high school where he served in the cadet corps attaining the rank of captain of company c and later lieutenant colonel and battalion commander he was called to duty in the united states army and was honorably discharged as a sergeant he joined the state planters bank of commerce and trust and served  years retiring from crestar bank while at the bank he completed the virginiamaryland school of bank management at the university of virginia the family will receive friends from  to  pm sunday september  at blileyscentral  augusta ave a memorial service will be held  am monday september  at centenary united methodist church  e grace st in lieu of flowers contributions may be made to the vmi foundation po box  lexington virginia   back to top guestbook  back to top services visitation blileys  central blileys  central  augusta ave richmond va us  map  directions visitation  blileys  central hazelgrove jr reginald bruce visitation  blileys  central  augusta ave richmond va   augusta ave richmond va  sunday september    pm   pm memorial service centenary united methodist church centenary united methodist church  e grace street richmond va us  map  directions service  centenary united methodist church hazelgrove jr reginald bruce service  centenary united methodist church  e grace street richmond va   e grace street richmond va  monday september    am  back to top please select the sections you wish to print   obituary text   main obitua